      "name": "Create or Modify System Process: Windows Service (AnyDesk)",
      "technique_id": "T1543.003",
      "description": "Install AnyDesk as a persistent Windows service on an internal host. Provides reliable remote access that survives reboots and user logoffs. Used as primary C2 channel throughout the operation.",
