      "modified": "2026-06-25T00:00:00.000Z",
      "name": "Exploitation for Privilege Escalation (BYOVD)",
      "technique_id": "T1068",
      "description": "Deploy ThrottleBlood.sys (vulnerable kernel driver derived from ThrottleStop.sys) via All.exe or Allpatch2.exe. Exploit the driver to gain kernel-level privileges, enabling termination of protected AV/EDR processes.",
      "confidence": 100,
      "effect_refs": [
