      "modified": "2026-06-25T00:00:00.000Z",
      "name": "Impair Defenses: Disable or Modify Tools",
      "technique_id": "T1562.001",
      "description": "Using kernel privileges from ThrottleBlood.sys, terminate all AV/EDR processes. Set global Windows Defender exclusions, disable real-time protection, and clean Defender cache and prefetch artifacts.",
