      "technique_id": "T1021.001",
      "description": "Spread across the environment using RDP (T1021.001), PsExec over SMB (T1021.002), and SSH/PuTTY (T1021.004). Compromise Windows servers, Linux hosts, and VMware ESXi systems. Establish footholds on backup servers and domain controllers.",
