      "modified": "2026-06-25T00:00:00.000Z",
      "name": "Data Destruction (VSS Deletion & Log Clearing)",
      "technique_id": "T1485",
      "description": "Delete all Volume Shadow Copies via 'vssadmin delete shadows /all' and 'wmic shadowcopy delete'. Forcibly terminate backup services, database services, and AV services. Clear Security/System/Application event logs via wevtutil. Delete RDP logs. Run self-delete batch script to remove attacker tooling.",
      "confidence": 100,
