      "modified": "2026-06-25T00:00:00.000Z",
      "name": "Data Encrypted for Impact",
      "technique_id": "T1486",
      "description": "Deploy Golang-based cross-platform ransomware encryptor via GPO/NETLOGON to all domain hosts simultaneously. Ransomware requires 8-byte password parameter at runtime. Encrypted files receive .7mtzhh or .ojuopo extension. README-GENTLEMEN.txt dropped in every directory with victim ID and TOX contact for ransom negotiation.",
      "confidence": 100,
